title: GoPro: Driven Series | Joey Logano Ep. 4
description:
In this episode of GoPro Original Series DRIVEN, take an in-depth look into the life of NASCAR driver and Daytona 500 champion, Joey Logano.  In addition to pushing the boundaries of a driver his age, discover how Joey hopes to use the racing platform to help better the lives of others.

Get stoked and subscribe: http://goo.gl/HgVXpQ

Music:

Ian Taggart
"Wilderness of Mirrors"
"Durant Manor"
"Respite"

Sadistik
"Exit Theme (-1)"

The Great Depression
"Lorraine Called, She Wants You to Work"

SIRSY
"Cannonball (Instrumental)"
